{"tid":885814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被日本傳媒追問本港新聞自由　林鄭月娥：應來香港親身感受","createTime":"2018-11-01T15:23:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T05:03:18.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e2f3510e5c5efe65f5922cd5d2c976101b9b800e","tid":885814,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T15:23:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1426178-20181101.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1426178-20181101.htm&d=pDHJKDQiVt9ZPbW1ih0ODv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=c4ea4df9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1426178-20181101.htm&h=1d432695\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1426178-20181101.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n正在日本東京訪問的行政長官林鄭月娥，被日本傳媒連番追問香港新聞自由情況、外國記者會副主席馬凱不獲續發工作簽證事件。<br />\n<br />\n對於香港的自由度排名在國際調查中跌至歷史新低，林鄭月娥回應，不可以控制外界的印象，但強調香港重視法治，市民享有自由及權利，呼籲記者親身感受香港的情況，不要受一些報道和印象所影響。"},{"pid":"00eb90c0f343cba2624bc7524ee9f4aab562011b","tid":885814,"uid":191815,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T15:24:27.000Z","msg":"唔好黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n被人捉去洗頭就玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"888ca3ecba7a367e2bb2e9cd0dbeeee36a37044f","tid":885814,"uid":154763,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T15:30:02.000Z","msg":"境都唔比入，點去感受？"},{"pid":"5d75cd6748cb8555e98aca70c02fb9211662ebc3","tid":885814,"uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"888ca3ecba7a367e2bb2e9cd0dbeeee36a37044f","tid":885814,"uid":154763,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T15:30:02.000Z","msg":"境都唔比入，點去感受？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T15:33:32.000Z","msg":"係機場感受"},{"pid":"e6e8f7cc88291ee2b3ec35923a79aa8a39492ebf","tid":885814,"uid":20563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":